Package: detectRUNS
Type: Package
Title: R Package to detect ROHom and ROHet in diploid genomes
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2016-07-11
Author: Filippo Biscarini
Maintainer: Filson <filippo.biscarini@ptp.it>
Description: Detection of RUNS of Homozygosity (ROHom) and of Heterozygosity (ROHet)
  a la Plink (see Bjelland et al. 2013).
